      "point": "Lack of computational cost analysis and unspecified model versions",
      "evidence": "No information regarding the computational resources... required for the few-shot amplification, distillation, and iterative backtranslation steps... The paper refers broadly to 'GPT-3 family models' and lacks specific model versions or API endpoint details."
